{"tid":1027342,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有生雞眼同疣既同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-02-18T18:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T23:07:44.000Z","uid":121544,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b28e71bd838a7586529683f8ebdd5961191b51","tid":1027342,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:11:16.000Z","msg":"由於之前做手術前上網睇過好多網都對依個病冇乜資料，加上果陣有好多巴絲都有俾意見我<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於此我喺度分享下我嘅經驗<br />\n希望可以幫到有依個病嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雞眼同疣好似，成日有人會分唔到邊個打邊個，佢地既分別可以睇下低張圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5itJri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5itJri.jpg&h=0b8a913b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個情況係由一粒唔理佢變到兩隻腳仲有手都係疣<br />\n平時去唔到啲要露腳既地方，因為<br />\n第一壓住壓住會痛<br />\n第二太核特，唔想俾啲fd見到<br />\n第三會傳染<br />\n<br />\n我生到咁起碼拖左五年<br />\n做冷凍手術洗左我四萬左右<br />\n好在保險有得cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我仲好記得果陣第一次去睇果個醫生仲話要打半身麻醉再用手術片啲疣出嚟，淨係手術費都9萬未計住院， 嗰陣嚇到我心都慌埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下係手術前既圖「慎入」<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/kzZkzs0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzZkzs0.jpg&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=1c2c088a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/kzZkzs0.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n你預做冷凍一定會痛，但長痛好過短痛<br />\n手術一定要做，如果唔係你會後悔<br />\n<br />\n以下幾點要特別注意<br />\n1.千奇唔好去剪佢，剪用出嚟既皮係有傳染性<br />\n2.掂完一定要洗手，如果唔係你預你手都會有<br />\n3.腳有係屋企一定要著拖鞋，如果唔係好大機會會傳染俾屋企人<br />\n4.發現自己有類似既嘢一定要睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n如果有咩問題都可以問我，我會盡量答我知道既嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e2f5e2cfc7e562cb3896792691fa9208275690","tid":1027342,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"我懷疑生左疣 但諗緊去睇醫生定自己整走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb46d0db970a60ff4cc4a2f5e43ea26f765a2a8","tid":1027342,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43e2f5e2cfc7e562cb3896792691fa9208275690","tid":1027342,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"我懷疑生左疣 但諗緊去睇醫生定自己整走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:30:40.000Z","msg":"睇醫生，整一粒300-700左右"},{"pid":"9cce5116a0a823221be6d8ec600f206d3546346b","tid":1027342,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e517d512e8b0389c1c849c50e1f334e6ec88daf","tid":1027342,"uid":1902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:42:19.000Z","msg":"生疣睇過醫生，<br />\n醫生話做凍殺3-4千到 (冇樓主幅圖咁嚴重),<br />\n我嫌貴得濟冇即時約做。<br />\n<br />\n然後去藥房問有冇d搽疣嘅藥水，<br />\n最後晚晚揸1個月好返晒，約30蚊支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議試左藥水先"},{"pid":"27afd45860ea43d6f53e5ec981a572942dbefbe7","tid":1027342,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cb46d0db970a60ff4cc4a2f5e43ea26f765a2a8","tid":1027342,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43e2f5e2cfc7e562cb3896792691fa9208275690","tid":1027342,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"我懷疑生左疣 但諗緊去睇醫生定自己整走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:30:40.000Z","msg":"睇醫生，整一粒300-700左右"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:44:31.000Z","msg":"但睇落又唔算好嚴重 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a5dc9e1560bf7b42007b549d0ef2d222fcf6f6","tid":1027342,"uid":1902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e517d512e8b0389c1c849c50e1f334e6ec88daf","tid":1027342,"uid":1902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:42:19.000Z","msg":"生疣睇過醫生，<br />\n醫生話做凍殺3-4千到 (冇樓主幅圖咁嚴重),<br />\n我嫌貴得濟冇即時約做。<br />\n<br />\n然後去藥房問有冇d搽疣嘅藥水，<br />\n最後晚晚揸1個月好返晒，約30蚊支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議試左藥水先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:46:41.000Z","msg":"補充返，係用過d凍殺疣立消都冇乜用先去睇醫生，<br />\n用藥水成效大好多"},{"pid":"1cd96845b2b36b0be760a98bf018bf049a95085b","tid":1027342,"uid":82940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:48:15.000Z","msg":"生過0.5cm x 0.5cm <br />\n搵針挑走黑點就冇事 重覆幾次 幾撚好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f25d78c836cd68ca41cf55f2797d6e77d2b1d8","tid":1027342,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be6bc8b648093821adc5716e08c2afc85625dd3","tid":1027342,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28f25d78c836cd68ca41cf55f2797d6e77d2b1d8","tid":1027342,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:33:42.000Z","msg":"咁多數都係疣"},{"pid":"538427b8587ae336f311d14508076c41d8147786","tid":1027342,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cd96845b2b36b0be760a98bf018bf049a95085b","tid":1027342,"uid":82940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:48:15.000Z","msg":"生過0.5cm x 0.5cm <br />\n搵針挑走黑點就冇事 重覆幾次 幾撚好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:34:00.000Z","msg":"岩岩生會易啲搞"},{"pid":"c2cedf3974c376254247ee8526aa312d2ebcc188","tid":1027342,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cce5116a0a823221be6d8ec600f206d3546346b","tid":1027342,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /