me":"2019-02-18T19:34:31.000Z","msg":"你真係好勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:39:04.000Z","msg":"我以為你自己辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw,如果好似我咁大忽，要自己搞真係唔知點算"},{"pid":"e9270a4bc5a910b036e512e7f2dba3d98337e1d7","tid":1027342,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:45:09.000Z","msg":"咁雞眼除咗唔治療仲可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1992130d580760c7156638638540830d9566eba","tid":1027342,"uid":92107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7b28e71bd838a7586529683f8ebdd5961191b51","tid":1027342,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:11:16.000Z","msg":"由於之前做手術前上網睇過好多網都對依個病冇乜資料，加上果陣有好多巴絲都有俾意見我<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於此我喺度分享下我嘅經驗<br />\n希望可以幫到有依個病嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雞眼同疣好似，成日有人會分唔到邊個打邊個，佢地既分別可以睇下低張圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5itJri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5itJri.jpg&h=0b8a913b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個情況係由一粒唔理佢變到兩隻腳仲有手都係疣<br />\n平時去唔到啲要露腳既地方，因為<br />\n第一壓住壓住會痛<br />\n第二太核特，唔想俾啲fd見到<br />\n第三會傳染<br />\n<br />\n我生到咁起碼拖左五年<br />\n做冷凍手術洗左我四萬左右<br />\n好在保險有得cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我仲好記得果陣第一次去睇果個醫生仲話要打半身麻醉再用手術片啲疣出嚟，淨係手術費都9萬未計住院， 嗰陣嚇到我心都慌埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下係手術前既圖「慎入」<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/kzZkzs0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzZkzs0.jpg&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=1c2c088a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/kzZkzs0.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n你預做冷凍一定會痛，但長痛好過短痛<br />\n手術一定要做，如果唔係你會後悔<br />\n<br />\n以下幾點要特別注意<br />\n1.千奇唔好去剪佢，剪用出嚟既皮係有傳染性<br />\n2.掂完一定要洗手，如果唔係你預你手都會有<br />\n3.腳有係屋企一定要著拖鞋，如果唔係好大機會會傳染俾屋企人<br />\n4.發現自己有類似既嘢一定要睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n如果有咩問題都可以問我，我會盡量答我知道既嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:50:19.000Z","msg":"我都有d, 之前只係腳得一兩粒，可能用手摸得多，手都有少少，有冇醫生推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntg: <a href=\"https://t.me/ducky2496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fducky2496&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=255d7666\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ducky2496</a>"},{"pid":"4e4da4a5d1116eb703c4301907ab0f51028f66d9","tid":1027342,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9be6bc8b648093821adc5716e08c2afc85625dd3","tid":1027342,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28f25d78c836cd68ca41cf55f2797d6e77d2b1d8","tid":1027342,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:33:42.000Z","msg":"咁多數都係疣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:54:16.000Z","msg":"但冇傳染性架喎"},{"pid":"cd6fbc002bd775416b60f3efba1958221a5af5a3","tid":1027342,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e4da4a5d1116eb703c4301907ab0f51028f66d9","tid":1027342,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9be6bc8b648093821adc5716e08c2afc85625dd3","tid":1027342,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28f25d78c836cd68ca41cf55f2797d6e77d2b1d8","tid":1027342,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:33:42.000Z","msg":"咁多數都係疣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:54:16.000Z","msg":"但冇傳染性架喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0